<item>
            <title>[LU-3061] (cl_lock.c:1964:discard_cb()) ASSERTION( (!(page-&gt;cp_type == CPT_CACHEABLE) || (!PageDirty(cl_page_vmpage(env, page)))) ) failed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3061</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This assertion happened when running Cray stress tests on a Lustre tag 2.3.63 compute client, running on SLES11 SP1 or SP2:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;    LustreError: 3661:0:(cl_lock.c:1964:discard_cb()) ASSERTION( (!(page-&amp;gt;cp_type == CPT_CACHEABLE) || (!PageDirty(cl_page_vmpage(env, page)))) ) failed:&lt;br/&gt;
    LustreError: 3661:0:(cl_lock.c:1964:discard_cb()) LBUG&lt;br/&gt;
    Pid: 3661, comm: ldlm_bl_00&lt;br/&gt;
    Call Trace:&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffff81007e59&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; try_stack_unwind+0x1a9/0x200&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffff81006625&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; dump_trace+0x95/0x300&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffffa01698d7&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; libcfs_debug_dumpstack+0x57/0x80 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;libcfs&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffffa0169e27&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; lbug_with_loc+0x47/0xb0 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;libcfs&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffffa02d48f0&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; discard_cb+0x160/0x1d0 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;obdclass&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffffa02d1c2f&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; cl_page_gang_lookup+0x1cf/0x3c0 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;obdclass&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffffa02d4652&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; cl_lock_discard_pages+0x112/0x1f0 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;obdclass&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffffa0695415&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; osc_lock_flush+0xf5/0x260 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;osc&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffffa0695661&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; osc_lock_cancel+0xe1/0x1c0 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;osc&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffffa02d246d&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; cl_lock_cancel0+0x6d/0x160 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;obdclass&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffffa02d31ab&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; cl_lock_cancel+0x13b/0x140 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;obdclass&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffffa06969cc&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; osc_ldlm_blocking_ast+0x20c/0x330 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;osc&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffffa03dea1b&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; ldlm_cancel_callback+0x6b/0x190 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;ptlrpc&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffffa03eca8a&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; ldlm_cli_cancel_local+0x8a/0x470 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;ptlrpc&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffffa03efd0c&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; ldlm_cli_cancel_list_local+0xec/0x280 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;ptlrpc&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffffa03f504c&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; ldlm_bl_thread_main+0x10c/0x420 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;ptlrpc&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffff81003efa&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; child_rip+0xa/0x20&lt;br/&gt;
    Kernel panic - not syncing: LBUG&lt;br/&gt;
    Pid: 3661, comm: ldlm_bl_00 Tainted: P           2.6.32.59-0.7.1_1.0000.6993-cray_gem_c #1&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The symptom is similar to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1442&quot; title=&quot;File corrupt with 1MiB-aligned 4k regions of zeros&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1442&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1442&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;/&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1680&quot; title=&quot;LBUG cl_lock.c:1949:discard_cb()) (ORI-726)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1680&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1680&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; but seems to be still happening. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Cray XT system, SLES11 SP1, SP2, Luster client 2.3, 2.4</environment>
