                            <comment id="55471" author="pjones" created="Thu, 4 Apr 2013 13:47:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;ok thanks Cory!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="55470" author="spitzcor" created="Thu, 4 Apr 2013 13:44:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Cray now believes that this bug is ours and that this ticket can be closed.  Our high-speed-network driver was leaving read-only pages marked as dirty, thus tripping the assertion.  Sorry for the report for a non-Lustre issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
